contents:
[workspace]
members = [ "foundations", "action-providers/functions", "action-providers/scripts",]

[package]
name = "textpieces-core"
version = "1.3.1"
edition = "2021"

[features]
glib = [ "textpieces-foundations/glib",]

[dependencies]
itertools = "0.12.0"
base64 = "0.22.0"
digest = "0.10.6"
fancy-regex = "0.13.0"
hex = "0.4.3"
html-escape = "0.2.13"
md5 = "0.7.0"
serde = "1.0.152"
serde_yaml = "0.9.17"
sha1 = "0.10.5"
sha2 = "0.10.6"
urlencoding = "2.1.2"
xml-rs = "0.8.4"
cpp_demangle = "0.4.4"
quoted_printable = "0.5.1"

[dev-dependencies]
pretty_assertions = "1.3.0"
test-strategy = "0.3.1"
proptest = "1.4.0"
once_cell = "1.17.0"
ctor = "0.2.8"
smol = "2.0.0"

[workspace.package]
version = "1.3.1"

[workspace.dependencies]
anyhow = "1.0.82"
thiserror = "1.0.59"
serde = "1.0.152"
smol = "2.0.0"

[dependencies.textpieces-foundations]
path = "foundations"

[dependencies.textpieces-function-actions]
path = "action-providers/functions"

[dependencies.textpieces-script-actions]
path = "action-providers/scripts"

[dependencies.serde_json]
version = "1.0.93"
features = [ "preserve_order",]

[dependencies.toml]
version = "0.8.14"
features = [ "preserve_order",]

[workspace.dependencies.textpieces-foundations]
path = "foundations"

[workspace.dependencies.serde_json]
version = "1.0.93"
features = [ "preserve_order",]

[workspace.dependencies.crossmist]
version = "1.0.4"

[package]
name = "textpieces-foundations"
version = "1.3.1"
edition = "2021"

[features]
glib = [ "dep:glib",]
crossmist = [ "dep:crossmist",]

[dependencies]
thiserror = "1.0.59"
enum-iterator = "2.0.1"

[dependencies.serde]
features = [ "derive",]
version = "1.0.152"

[dependencies.glib]
version = "0.19.2"
optional = true

[dependencies.crossmist]
optional = true
version = "1.0.4"

[package]
name = "textpieces-function-actions"
version = "1.3.1"
edition = "2021"

[dependencies]
derive-debug = "0.1.2"
smol = "2.0.0"
anyhow = "1.0.82"
scopeguard = "1.2.0"

[dependencies.textpieces-foundations]
features = [ "crossmist",]
path = "foundations"

[dependencies.crossmist]
features = [ "smol",]
version = "1.0.4"

[dependencies.procspawn]
version = "1.0.0"
features = [ "ctor",]

[package]
name = "textpieces-script-actions"
version = "1.3.1"
edition = "2021"

[dependencies]
thiserror = "1.0.59"
anyhow = "1.0.82"
smol = "2.0.0"

[dependencies.textpieces-foundations]
path = "foundations"

[dependencies.serde]
features = [ "derive",]
version = "1.0.152"

[dependencies.serde_json]
version = "1.0.93"
features = [ "preserve_order",]

[dependencies.rustix]
version = "0.38.34"
features = [ "process",]
